transcripts.text: I now turn this over to the new team, starting with our next Secretary of Treasury, Janet Yellen.  Again, Janet, thanks for accepting.
I think they're going to clean this off for us here.

Thank you, Mr.  President-elect and Madam Vice President-elect.  It's my great honor to have this opportunity to serve you and the American people and to join this incredible economic team at this moment of great challenge for our country.  They're really showing themselves to do really well.  Come on, man.
